2.8.5 | 2023-08-14 | raj | STRY0136615 - STRETCH-PLACEHOLDER- Header UI Control (updates to add lable and change the style for label and text)</description>
        <media_type/>
        <name>dtechTaskerFiles.html</name>
        <scoped_name>x_153465_discovert_dtechTaskerFiles.html</scoped_name>
        <sys_class_name>sys_ui_macro</sys_class_name>
        <sys_created_by>rjoy</sys_created_by>
